snippet.title: The Interplay 3DO Buffet - 3DO Demo Disc Tour
snippet.description:
It's A Smorgasbord For Your Mind Sample Seven Tasty Games.

Casper (Video)
Cyberia (Rolling Demo)
Kingdom - The Far Reaches (Playable)
Another World / Out of this World (Playable)
Waterworld (Video) - Cancelled game
Alone in the Dark 2 (Playable)
Wolfenstein 3D (Playable)

Kingdom - The Far Reaches, 3DO Buffet (C) Interplay
Ports of Wolfenstein 3D and Kingdom by Logicware
Wolfenstein 3D (C) Zenimax, Bethesda, id Software, Xbox Game Studios
Casper movie and Waterworld (C) Universal
Casper game developed by Funcom
Another World developed by Delphine Software
Alone in the Dark 2 (C) Embracer Group, THQ Nordic
AitD 2 originally developed by Inforgrames. Ported to 3DO by Krysalis
